14/*! \file */
15
16#include <config.h>
17
18#include <dns/fixedname.h>
19
20void
21dns_fixedname_init(dns_fixedname_t *fixed) {
22 dns_name_init(&fixed->name, fixed->offsets);
23 isc_buffer_init(&fixed->buffer, fixed->data, DNS_NAME_MAXWIRE);
24 dns_name_setbuffer(&fixed->name, &fixed->buffer);
25}
26
27void
28dns_fixedname_invalidate(dns_fixedname_t *fixed) {
29 dns_name_invalidate(&fixed->name);
30}
31
32dns_name_t *
33dns_fixedname_name(dns_fixedname_t *fixed) {
34 return (&fixed->name);
35}
36
37dns_name_t *
38dns_fixedname_initname(dns_fixedname_t *fixed) {
39 dns_fixedname_init(fixed);
40 return (dns_fixedname_name(fixed));
41}
